## Ques: Take positive integer input and tell if it is even or odd

explanation:- 

is divisible by 2 - even
↳ is not divisible by 2-odd

n=8
if(n%2 == 0) 

 8%2 
  ↓ 
  0
condition
ture 

Code:- 

#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main(){
cout<<"Enter a number : ";
int n;
cin>>n;
if(n%2==0){
cout<<"Even";
}
else{
cout<<"Odd";
}
}
